    <item>
      <title>Uncovering the origins of inner speech sensory content</title>
      <link>/talk/2023-jcep/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Jan 2023 10:30:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/talk/2023-jcep/</guid>
      <description>


&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Abstract&lt;/em&gt;: Inner speech is accompanied by a subjective multisensory experience. However, the origins (causes) of this subjective experience are debated. In this study, we used transcranial magnetic stimulation to disentangle the predictions of competing theoretical frameworks.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
